We're proud to announce tDAR's twelfth production release: Lithic.  This release contains numerous bug fixes, performance enhancements, and security related improvements.  Some specific highlights include: improvements to the new user, purchase, and file download processes; improvements that allow users to provide feedback to a contributor or request access to a record.; the ability to duplicate existing resources; and <a href="http://www.tdar.org/news/2014/08/tdar-software-update-lithic/">much more</a>.